window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When an elf crashes Santa's sleigh into Mike Radley's living room, he doesn't know what to expect.</p> <p>He didn't expect a one-way trip to the North Pole where Jack Frost is waiting to kill him.</p> <p>He really didn't expect the Grim Reaper and Lily the succubus to take over Santa's gift delivering duties.</p> <p>And he definitely didn't expect to get caught up in the centuries-long battle between Santa Claus and the Krampus</p> <p>Will Mike save Christmas in time, or will he just end up on the naughty list?</p> <p>Merry Christmas. Expect the Unexpected.</p>"; 
